<p>Local SEO costs less because the target area is smaller. Fewer keywords. Less content. Lower competition for most markets.</p>
<p>For local service businesses, the combination of <a href="/blog/build-online-presence-local-business/">blog SEO and local SEO</a> delivers the highest ROI. Blog content builds <a href="/glossary/topical-authority/">topical authority</a>. GBP posts keep your profile active. Together, they compound.</p>
